# Documentation Rules

## Code Documentation
- Document all public methods and classes
- Use proper PHPDoc comments
- Document complex business logic
- Use TypeScript types for better documentation
- Keep documentation up to date

## API Documentation
- Document all API endpoints
- Use proper API documentation tools
- Document request/response formats
- Document authentication requirements
- Keep API documentation up to date

## Project Documentation
- Keep README.md up to date
- Document project setup
- Document deployment process
- Document development workflow
- Document project architecture

## Component Documentation
- Document component props and emits
- Document component usage
- Document component examples
- Document component styling
- Keep component documentation up to date

## General Documentation
- Use proper documentation tools
- Keep documentation organized
- Use proper documentation format
- Document all important decisions
- Follow documentation best practices
